More bad news for Boeing.

The aviation giant（航空巨头）
which used to be one of America’s crown jewels（皇冠上的明珠）
facing a massive shakeup（人事调整）.

CEO Dave Calhoun announcing he’ll be stepping down（下台）
as the company faces growing safety concerns
surrounding their fleet of planes（一堆飞机）.
As well as an ongoing whistleblower（吹哨人） investigation.

